track_notes: This is the shortest route to the summit. Follow the paved road until the end, to the Bom Retiro shelter. There the trail begins. You can drive to Bom Retiro and start the trail walking from there. The trail is well marked and with signposts. But take the GPS anyway!
This route gives access to two SOTA peaks, Pedra do Conde and Pico da Tijuca.
track_title: Route to Pedra do Conde and Pico da Tijuca
